race.comment: ANNANDA (7) bounced back to form with a third place run at this track after a less-than-encouraging seventh at Balaklava two back. Further improvement can see her in the finish. CAPTAIN LOVE (1) is rock hard fit for recent racing and looks an each-way chance on his best. He can roll forward and give himself a chance near the speed. The market keeps finding FLAMING EYES (9) and she keeps racing well without winning. She got a wide draw but she gets Holder on and can be in the finish. YOUBEEFORTY (6) looks a genuine top-three chance if things go his way. Placed second by a neck last start at Mildura and should race on the speed, in the mix.
